  "name": "RPlog_An_Unexpected_Visitor",
  "title": "An Unexpected Visitor",
  "summary": "During the Winter Fete aboard the NRSD Reprisal, pilots Kesander 'Sandman' and the rookie Raxis are scrambled to intercept the freighter Valspar, which is squawking an invalid transponder over Mon Calamari space. Joined by the quiet veteran Kyrin in Ghost One, the trio of X-wings pursues the fleeing ship as its pilot Mitler dodges through orbital barge traffic and stalls with feeble excuses. When warning shots fail, Mitler vents his cargo to scatter the fighters and opens fire before slipping out of the gravity well and jumping to hyperspace just ahead of the Ghosts' guns. Though the Valspar escapes, it abandons a heavily shielded, pressurized cargo container the pilots suspect may hold trafficked sentients. Sandman calls for salvage shuttles, and the relieved Ghost flight, all three pilots intact, sets course home for fish sandwiches.",
